   "source": [
    "{\n",
    " \"cells\": [\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"markdown\",\"metadata\":{},\"source\":[\"# Procurement Document Analyzer\\n\",\"**NLP Project 83 of 100** — Compare vendor proposals by extracting key terms, pricing, and requirements.\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"import re, numpy as np, pandas as pd, matplotlib.pyplot as plt\\nimport warnings; warnings.filterwarnings('ignore')\\n%matplotlib inline\\nprint('Loaded.')\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"proposals = [\\n    {'vendor':'Vendor A','text':'Cloud hosting services. Price: $5,000/month. SLA: 99.9% uptime. Support: 24/7. Contract: 12 months. Includes 500GB storage and unlimited bandwidth.'},\\n    {'vendor':'Vendor B','text':'Managed cloud infrastructure. Price: $4,200/month. SLA: 99.5% uptime. Support: Business hours only. Contract: 24 months. Includes 1TB storage and 10TB bandwidth.'},\\n    {'vendor':'Vendor C','text':'Enterprise cloud platform. Price: $6,500/month. SLA: 99.99% uptime. Support: 24/7 dedicated. Contract: 12 months. Includes 2TB storage, unlimited bandwidth, and DR.'},\\n]\\n\\ndef analyze_proposal(proposal):\\n    text = proposal['text']\\n    price = re.search(r'\\\\$(\\\\d[\\\\d,]*)', text)\\n    sla = re.search(r'(\\\\d+\\\\.\\\\d+)%', text)\\n    contract = re.search(r'(\\\\d+)\\\\s*months', text)\\n    support = re.search(r'Support:\\\\s*(.+?)(?:\\\\.|$)', text)\\n    return {\\n        'Vendor': proposal['vendor'],\\n        'Price/mo': f'${price.group(1)}' if price else 'N/A',\\n        'SLA': f'{sla.group(1)}%' if sla else 'N/A',\\n        'Contract': f'{contract.group(1)} months' if contract else 'N/A',\\n        'Support': support.group(1).strip() if support else 'N/A',\\n    }\\n\\nresults = [analyze_proposal(p) for p in proposals]\\ndf = pd.DataFrame(results)\\nprint(df.to_string(index=False))\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"# Visual comparison\\nprices = [int(re.search(r'\\\\d[\\\\d,]*',r['Price/mo']).group().replace(',','')) for r in results]\\nfig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(8,4))\\nax.bar([r['Vendor'] for r in results], prices, color=['steelblue','coral','seagreen'])\\nax.set_title('Monthly Price Comparison'); ax.set_ylabel('$/month')\\nplt.tight_layout(); plt.show()\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"markdown\",\"metadata\":{},\"source\":[\"## Summary\\n\",\"- **Automated proposal analysis extracts key comparison metrics.**\\n\",\"- **Regex-based extraction handles structured procurement text effectively.**\\n\",\"- **For production, add scoring/ranking** based on weighted criteria.\\n\",\"- **LLMs can summarize strengths/weaknesses** of each proposal.\"]}\n",
    " ],\n",
